      "content": "a perforated eardrum? that sounds scary. but u said it's not a cause for concern... if it's just a little fluid or a small tear, surely it'll just heal itself over the next day or two? i really don't want to deal with the doctor right now, it's such a hassle. can i just wait it out and see if it clears up by tomorrow?",
